> > -----Original Message-----
> > From: cmeanley [mailto:cmeanley_at_pacificcoast_dot_net]
> > Sent: Friday, March 29, 2002 10:37 AM
> > To: Mike Benthin; Phillip Rose
> > Cc: type2_at_type2_dot_com
